		<xsd:annotation>
			<xsd:documentation source="http://www.openapplications.org/oagis/10">The purpose of the ChangePaymentStatus is to enable an application to request specific PaymentStatus information to be Changeed by another business application module.

This typically a transaction that occurs between a company and a Bank in order to remit PaymentStatus to company that has provided goods or services.  

The response to the ChangePaymentStatus is the AcknowledgePaymentStatus.</xsd:documentation>
		</xsd:annotation>
	</xsd:element>
